{"tid":328141,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"除左茶記既凍檸茶 其他野飲都睇唔上眼","createTime":"2017-07-19T10:57:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-19T14:56:25.000Z","uid":6739,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"014b805cdaead6c8c5a70d7c8cf0c22cf86bc156","tid":328141,"uid":6739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T10:57:27.000Z","msg":"隨住飲品既種類越來越多<br />\n選擇就越來越少<br />\n大多數都粗製濫造<br />\n無樣岩飲<br />\n<br />\n入到惠康七仔行一個圈都無野買得落手<br />\n直到去茶記食個飯<br />\n叫返杯冰凍既凍檸茶<br />\n個種澀味同檸檬味再加埋唔同茶記既茶底交滙埋一齊<br />\n先至令我人生有返啲希望<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家又有咩睇法？<br />\n<br />\n人生啊....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a9bf532d418322cb5d1ff64d0f47a1cf2f60183","tid":328141,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T10:58:59.000Z","msg":"茶記啲茶 好多煲過火"},{"pid":"d3b99612b7453faa13ae3bacec2f758ec7d7ff25","tid":328141,"uid":6739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T11:23:50.000Z","msg":"無人飲檸茶？"},{"pid":"59863bfcb5bd42fc2d82c1743c0ad00594b5eab8","tid":328141,"uid":103499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T11:38:10.000Z","msg":"咁凍奶茶呢，我鍾意飲茶記果d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呀"},{"pid":"24100f2f41ef2087337704deaf94ea9116bfef92","tid":328141,"uid":1496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T11:39:16.000Z","msg":"檸茶小甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46ec7448be42317e0b248ce428a2ec939985853c","tid":328141,"uid":13257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T11:40:25.000Z","msg":"凍奶茶呢"},{"pid":"8bd7104df4de7ab454070510d5aaca11dfe8beea","tid":328141,"uid":6739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T12:03:48.000Z","msg":"凍奶茶都曾經迷過一排<br />\n直到有排覺得淡奶好肥就無飲<br />\n<br />\n都係檸茶好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85ced92faa7efce3b210dc82939a4ea3e848fade","tid":328141,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T12:04:44.000Z","msg":"唔覺好正"},{"pid":"fa23d744999bad7e840289ac672d5f0031d8b4e2","tid":328141,"uid":30410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T14:56:25.000Z","msg":"自從去過一間垃圾茶記飲左杯有啡味既凍檸茶後淨係會飲茶走"}]}